txt.en: 'The second ingredient I need are a number of sprigs of recently cut mistletoe. You can likely find it hanging in the forest to the north of here.'
Bring the mistletoe to Enit at Galar Culch
'This mistletoe is fresh enough, place it here. Do you have the rest?'
'This mistletoe is fresh enough, place it here. Do you have the rest?'
Enit has asked you to retrieve several sprigs of mistletoe as part of a ritual to summon one of the spirits of the forest.
The mistletoe Enit has requested can be gathered in the forest across the river to the north-west.
Bring the mistletoe to Enit at Galar Culch
Enit is at Galar Culch in the Mournshaws.\n\nYou should bring the mistletoe you have collected to Enit.
